name: Data Hygiene
description: Dashboards & Searches designed to detect common issues when onboarding data, specifically timestamp detection and multi-line event configuration.

panels.name: Event Fingerprint Count by SC.
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory=*
| parse regex "^(?<fingerprint>.{20})"
| count BY fingerprint, _sourceCategory
// Replace alphabet
| toLowerCase(fingerprint) AS fingerprint
| replace(fingerprint,"a","w") AS fingerprint | replace(fingerprint,"b","w") AS fingerprint | replace(fingerprint,"c","w") AS fingerprint | replace(fingerprint,"d","w") AS fingerprint | replace(fingerprint,"e","w") AS fingerprint | replace(fingerprint,"f","w") AS fingerprint | replace(fingerprint,"g","w") AS fingerprint | replace(fingerprint,"h","w") AS fingerprint | replace(fingerprint,"i","w") AS fingerprint | replace(fingerprint,"j","w") AS fingerprint | replace(fingerprint,"a","w") AS fingerprint | replace(fingerprint,"b","w") AS fingerprint | replace(fingerprint,"c","w") AS fingerprint | replace(fingerprint,"d","w") AS fingerprint | replace(fingerprint,"e","w") AS fingerprint | replace(fingerprint,"f","w") AS fingerprint | replace(fingerprint,"g","w") AS fingerprint | replace(fingerprint,"h","w") AS fingerprint | replace(fingerprint,"i","w") AS fingerprint | replace(fingerprint,"j","w") AS fingerprint | replace(fingerprint,"k","w") AS fingerprint | replace(fingerprint,"l","w") AS fingerprint | replace(fingerprint,"m","w") AS fingerprint | replace(fingerprint,"n","w") AS fingerprint | replace(fingerprint,"o","w") AS fingerprint | replace(fingerprint,"p","w") AS fingerprint | replace(fingerprint,"q","w") AS fingerprint | replace(fingerprint,"r","w") AS fingerprint | replace(fingerprint,"s","w") AS fingerprint | replace(fingerprint,"t","w") AS fingerprint | replace(fingerprint,"u","w") AS fingerprint | replace(fingerprint,"v","w") AS fingerprint | replace(fingerprint,"w","w") AS fingerprint | replace(fingerprint,"x","w") AS fingerprint | replace(fingerprint,"y","w") AS fingerprint | replace(fingerprint,"z","w") AS fingerprint
// Replace numeric
| replace(fingerprint,"1","d") AS fingerprint | replace(fingerprint,"2","d") AS fingerprint | replace(fingerprint,"3","d") AS fingerprint | replace(fingerprint,"4","d") AS fingerprint | replace(fingerprint,"5","d") AS fingerprint | replace(fingerprint,"6","d") AS fingerprint | replace(fingerprint,"7","d") AS fingerprint | replace(fingerprint,"8","d") AS fingerprint | replace(fingerprint,"9","d") AS fingerprint | replace(fingerprint,"0","d") AS fingerprint
// Replace whitespace
| replace(fingerprint," ","S") AS fingerprint
| sum(_count) AS events BY fingerprint, _sourceCategory
| count BY _sourceCategory
| sort _count

panels.name: Ingest Difference gt. 1hr by SC.
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory=*
| _receipttime - _messagetime AS delta
| floor(abs(delta/3600000)) AS offset_hr
| where offset_hr > 0
| count BY _sourceCategory, offset_hr
| sort _count

panels.name: Avg. Ingest Lag by Collector (secs)
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory=*
| _receipttime - _messagetime AS delta_ms
| delta_ms/1000 AS delta_sec
| timeslice 1m
| avg(delta_sec) AS delta_sec_avg BY _timeslice, _collector
| transpose row _timeslice column _collector

panels.name: Neg. Ingest Delta by SN.
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory=*
| _receipttime - _messagetime AS delta_ms
| delta_ms/1000 AS delta_sec
| where delta_sec < 0
| avg(delta_sec) AS avg_sec, count BY _sourceName, _sourceCategory
| sort avg_sec asc

panels.name: Autocorrected Timestamps by SC.
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory=*
| count BY _sourceCategory, _format
| parse regex field=_format "(?:t:)?(?<type>\w+)(?::o:(?<offset>\d+):l:(?<length>\d+):p:(?<date_format>.*))?" nodrop
| where type matches "ac*"
| fields - _format, offset, length, _some_matched
| sort _count

panels.name: Ingest Lag by Collector (secs)
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory=*
| _receipttime - _messagetime AS delta_ms
| delta_ms/1000 AS delta_sec
| max(delta_sec), min(delta_sec), pct(delta_sec,25,50,75) BY _collector

panels.name: Avg. Ingest Lag by Source Category (secs)
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory=*
| _receipttime - _messagetime AS delta_ms
| delta_ms/1000 AS delta_sec
| timeslice 1m
| avg(delta_sec) AS delta_sec_avg BY _timeslice, _sourceCategory
| transpose row _timeslice column _sourceCategory

panels.name: Avg. Ingest Lag by Source Name (secs)
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory=*
| _receipttime - _messagetime AS delta_ms
| delta_ms/1000 AS delta_sec
| timeslice 1m
| avg(delta_sec) AS delta_sec_avg BY _timeslice, _sourceName
| transpose row _timeslice column _sourceName
